{
  "texts": [
    "Tool invocations span single-step and multi-step action generation, covering eight subtasks, including open weather and webshop.",
    "The research and application of LLMs as AI Agents, exemplified by entities like AutoGPT foot_46 and AgentGPT foot_47, are continuously advancing.",
    "Agent evaluation datasets specifically concentrate on the capabilities of LLMs functioning as Agents.",
    "Agent-Bench (Liu et al, 2023f) undergoes assessment within English scenarios.",
    "It stands out as the inaugural benchmark designed to evaluate the performance of LLM-as-Agent across various environments, encompassing eight distinct settings and providing a thorough examination of LLMs' competence as independent agents."
  ]
}